      "question": "At rest, a normal healthy muscle should exhibit:",
      "options": [
        "Continuous fibrillations",
        "Fasciculation potentials",
        "Electrical silence",
        "High frequency discharges"
      ],
      "answer": "Electrical silence",
      "explanation": "In a relaxed state without active motor neuron firing, a healthy muscle displays a baseline of complete electrical silence."
